'''八氯萘'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>10</sub>Cl<sub>8</sub>。它是难溶于水的黄色固体<ref name=GESTIS>{{cite web|url=https://gestis.dguv.de/data?name=112115|title=Octachlornaphthalin|publisher=GESTIS-Stoffdatenbank|accessdate=2020-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Jeanne Mager Stellman|title=Encyclopaedia of Occupational Health and Safety|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e4_S46UcI2AC&pg=PA298|year=1998|publisher=International Labour Organization|isbn=978-92-2-109817-1|pages=298}}</ref>，于2015年作为多氯萘列入[[斯德哥爾摩公約|斯德哥爾摩公約]]附录A和附录C中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chm.pops.int/theconvention/thepops/allpops/tabid/2509/|title=All POPs listed in the Stockholm Convention|publisher=UN environment programme|accessdate=2020-01-09|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209132009/http://chm.pops.int/TheConvention/ThePOPs/AllPOPs/tabid/2509/|dead-url=no}}</ref>它可由[[萘|萘]]在[[磺酰氯|磺酰氯]]中在[[氯化铁|氯化铁]]的存在下和[[氯气|氯气]]反应制得<ref>{{cite book|author1=I.L. Knunyants|author2=G.G. Yakobson|title=Syntheses of Fluoroorganic Compounds|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=m6zxCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA114|date=6 December 2012|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-642-70207-5|pages=114}}</ref>；或由萘和[[氯气|氯气]]在[[五氯化锑|五氯化锑]]的存在下于150~210 °C反应得到。<ref>{{cite book|title=Houben-Weyl Methods of Organic Chemistry Vol. V/3, 4th Edition: Fluorine and Chlorine Compounds|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aTSGAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA670|date=14 May 2014|publisher=Georg Thieme Verlag|isbn=978-3-13-179994-4|pages=670}}</ref>它和[[乙硫醇钠|乙硫醇钠]]在[[二甲基甲酰胺|DMF]]中反应，可以得到八(乙硫基)萘。<ref>Mayer, Roland; Decker, Daniel; Kniess, Torsten; Lang, Reinhard. Nucleophilic substitution of octachloronaphthalene with organothiolates. ''Zeitschrift fuer Chemie'', 1990. 30 (11): 404-405. ISSN: 0044-2402.</ref>它在45~50 °C可以被[[五氟化钒|五氟化钒]]氧化，得到C<sub>10</sub>Cl<sub>8</sub>F<sub>8</sub>和[[四氟化钒|VF<sub>4</sub>]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Fluorine Chemistry|volume=125|issue=10|language=en|date=2004-10|pages=1411–1414|doi=10.1016/j.jfluchem.2004.01.013|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113904000338|title=Fluorine addition to polychlorinated and polybrominated ethenes and arenes using vanadium pentafluoride|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Vadim V. Bardin, Svetlana G. Bardina|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622160807/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113904000338|dead-url=no}}</ref>
